### Test Transform Interceptor - CamelCase Response
### 
### Sau khi start server, chạy các tests này để verify responses đã là camelCase

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Test GET workspaces (should return camelCase)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workspaces
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected response:
### [
###   {
###     "id": "...",
###     "ownerId": "...",        // ✅ camelCase (was owner_id)
###     "createdAt": "...",      // ✅ camelCase (was created_at)
###     "updatedAt": "..."       // ✅ camelCase (was updated_at)
###   }
### ]


### 2. Test GET projects (should return camelCase)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?workspaceId=YOUR_WORKSPACE_ID
